gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Thunder 119, Jazz 107
gameRecap.excerpt: The Thunder win their third straight game to improve to 48-20 as they defeated the Jazz, 119-107. Chet Holmgren led the Thunder with 35 points, 14 rebounds, and three blocks as Shai Gilgeous-Alexander added 31 points and seven assists, in his 50th 30-PT game of the year. Collin Sexton led the Jazz with 25 points, five rebounds, and seven assists, as Utah falls to 29-40 on the year. OKC moves 0.5 games up on DEN in the Western Conference.
